And further, in the ſame Booke, and ſame Article, hee ſayth:


Yea, I am ſure, that you will grant; that if God doe Predeſtinate a man, to doe things raſhly, and without any deliberation, He ſhall not Deliberate at all; but runne headlong upon it;


bee it Good or Evill, that hee, doth.
